message: Hello Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe could significantly enhance your business operations or personal projects. Given its unique features and capabilities, I estimate its true value to be well above $15000. Considering this, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $20000. This is a special opportunity to acquire a high-quality asset at a competitive rate. If you're interested, please let me know so we can proceed with the transaction.
